user.bio: Travelling the world one beer at a time!

items.badge_description: At first taste, dark ales can be overwhelming for even the most skilled of beer drinkers, but your will is weak and with time you will eventually turn to the dark side. That's 105 different beers with the style of Dark Ale, Belgian Strong Dark Ale, Lager - Euro Dark, Lager - Dark, IPA - Black / Cascadian Dark Ale or IPA - Imperial / Double Black.. Try 5 more for Level 22!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 310 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 63!

With a bitter bite and a toasted maltiness, this dark style is a perfect combination to be enjoyed any time, day or night. That's 15 different beers with the style of IPA - Black / Cascadian Dark Ale or IPA - Imperial / Double Black. Try 5 more for Level 4!
